  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>(Requires attunement by a bard, cleric, or druid)</em></p><p>This staff has 10 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 or more of its charges to cast one of the following spells from it, using your spell save DC and spellcasting ability modifier: @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.Item.uUWb1wZgtMou0TVP]{Cure Wounds} (1 charge per spell level, up to 4th), @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.Item.F0GsG0SJzsIOacwV]{Lesser Restoration} (2 charges), or @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.Item.Pyzmm8R7rVsNAPsd]{Mass Cure Wounds} (5 charges).</p><p>The staff regains 1d6 + 4 expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the staff vanishes in a flash of light, lost forever.</p>",
